text={
[1]={
ja={
{
"その夜は、満月だった。",
},
},
en={
{
"Tonight is a full moon.",
},
},
},
[2]={
ja={
{
"満月のおかげで、夜空は明るい。",
},
},
en={
{
"As such, the sky was clear.",
},
},
},
[3]={
ja={
{
"おかげでこの時間でもグラウンドは闇に覆われておらず、土砂による整備がしやすかった。",
},
},
en={
{
"With the sports grounds visible under the light, Sahara had an easy time tidying up the grounds.",
},
},
},
[4]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00175",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（奇跡の行使……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(Using my miracle...)",
},
},
},
[5]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00176",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（僕はこの行為で、生徒のために働いているつもりだった……心残りを、少しでも解消するために）",
},
},
en={
{
"(I've been trying to lend a hand to the students... to alleviate my regret if even by a little.)",
},
},
},
[6]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00177",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（ですが……逆に、心残りが募ったようにも思います）",
},
},
en={
{
"(But... I feel like my regrets have only grown.)",
},
},
},
[7]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00178",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（なぜ僕は、生前のうちから、こうした行為ができなかったのだろうかと……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(Why couldn't I have done this when I was alive...?)",
},
},
},
[8]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00179",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（こんなふうに、どうしても後悔が生まれてしまう……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(Where's this sense of remorse coming from...?)",
},
},
},
[9]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00180",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（この後悔こそが……空に還るための、最大の障害なのかもしれませんね）",
},
},
en={
{
"(This is likely... what's keeping me from returning to the heavens.)",
},
},
},
[10]={
ja={
{
"魂人とは、生前の後悔と向き合うために、現世に留まり続けている存在なのかもしれない。",
},
},
en={
{
"Tamabito may be being kept in the living world in order to face their regrets.",
},
},
},
[11]={
ja={
{
"だがそれは、人間も同じだ。",
},
},
en={
{
"But that applies to humans as well.",
},
},
},
[12]={
ja={
{
"人間もまた、過去の後悔と向き合うために、生きているのかもしれないのだ。",
},
},
en={
{
"Humans may as well live in order to face the regrets from their past.",
},
},
},
[13]={
ja={
{
"砂原の脳裏に浮かぶのは、後悔の源泉である家族と。",
},
},
en={
{
"Sahara's mind was filled with thoughts of his family, the source of his regrets.",
},
},
},
[14]={
ja={
{
"そして、魂人の自分を救ってくれた学園長のことだ。",
},
},
en={
{
"And of the principal who had saved him, a tamabito.",
},
},
},
[15]={
ja={
{
"学園長は今、秘密裏に進めていた計画を、中止せざるを得ない状況におちいっている。",
},
},
en={
{
"At present, she's backed into a corner where she has no choice but to put a stop to the secret project she'd been working on.",
},
},
},
[16]={
ja={
{
"そのせいで迷い、悩み、苦しんでいる。",
},
},
en={
{
"So she's been lost, worried, and suffering.",
},
},
},
[17]={
ja={
{
"ならば、賛同者である自分も力になりたい。",
},
},
en={
{
"As her compatriot, he wanted to help her.",
},
},
},
[18]={
ja={
{
"そのためにも、まだ自分は還るべきではない。",
},
},
en={
{
"So he couldn't allow himself to go back yet.",
},
},
},
[19]={
ja={
{
"いや……。",
},
},
en={
{
"No...",
},
},
},
[20]={
ja={
{
"もしかしたら、逆なのだろうか。",
},
},
en={
{
"Perhaps it's the other way around.",
},
},
},
[21]={
ja={
{
"自分が還ることで初めて、学園長に恩を返すことができるのだろうか……。",
},
},
en={
{
"Going back may be the first step in repaying his debt to her...",
},
},
},
[22]={
ja={
{
"学園長の決断次第によっては、町の魂人の多くが敵になる。",
},
},
en={
{
"Her decision may turn the tamabito of the town against her.",
},
},
},
[23]={
ja={
{
"国魂人であるオトヒメも。",
},
},
en={
{
"Including Otohime.",
},
},
},
[24]={
ja={
{
"そして、魂人の味方をするだろう、風見蒼空も……。",
},
},
en={
{
"And even Kazami Sora, an ally of tamabito...",
},
},
},
[25]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00181",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（だとしても……僕は……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(But even so... I...)",
},
},
},
[26]={
ja={
{
"自分は最後まで、学園長の味方をする。",
},
},
en={
{
"He would be on the principal's side.",
},
},
},
[27]={
ja={
{
"恩義があるから。その恩は家族愛にも劣らないから。",
},
},
en={
{
"His obligation to her was as strong as one would have for their family.",
},
},
},
[28]={
ja={
{
"だから、どんなに恨まれても。",
},
},
en={
{
"So no matter how much they may despise him.",
},
},
},
[29]={
ja={
{
"愛する生徒――魂人の教え子たちに、恨まれても。",
},
},
en={
{
"Even if his dear tamabito students come to despite him.",
},
},
},
[30]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00182",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（それでも僕は……学園長の、味方でありたい）",
},
},
en={
{
"(I... want to support madam principal.)",
},
},
},
[31]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00183",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（この気持ちは変わらない……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(My feelings haven't changed...)",
},
},
},
[32]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00184",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"（たとえ……なにがあったとしても……）",
},
},
en={
{
"(No matter... what may come of this...)",
},
},
},
[33]={
name={name="？？？",ja="？？？",en="???"},
ja={
{
"「…………」",
},
},
en={
{
"「......」",
},
},
},
[34]={
ja={
{
"そのとき。",
},
},
en={
{
"That was when.",
},
},
},
[35]={
ja={
{
"満月が、雲に隠れた。",
},
},
en={
{
"Clouds covered up the full moon.",
},
},
},
[36]={
ja={
{
"月明かりを失い、視界が閉ざされる中で。",
},
},
en={
{
"In this closed world, robbed of its light.",
},
},
},
[37]={
ja={
{
"砂原の前に、漆黒の人影が現れた。",
},
},
en={
{
"A pitch-black shadow appeared before Sahara.",
},
},
},
[38]={
ja={
{
"まるで、待ち構えていたかのように。",
},
},
en={
{
"As if it were waiting for him.",
},
},
},
[39]={
ja={
{
"この時間、この場所で、砂原を待つことができる人物など、限られている……。",
},
},
en={
{
"There weren't many people that could wait on him at this time and place...",
},
},
},
[40]={
name={name="？？？",ja="？？？",en="???"},
ja={
{
"「…………」",
},
},
en={
{
"「......」",
},
},
},
[41]={
ja={
{
"その者は、言葉を発した。",
},
},
en={
{
"The figure said something.",
},
},
},
[42]={
ja={
{
"詠み出すのは、聞き覚えのある",
{"ruby",text="のりと"},
"祝詞",
{"/ruby"},
"……。",
},
},
en={
{
"It was an invocation that he had heard somewhere before...",
},
},
},
[43]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00185",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「ああ……そうですか」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Aah... I see.」",
},
},
},
[44]={
ja={
{
"砂原は、すべてを理解した。",
},
},
en={
{
"Sahara understood everything.",
},
},
},
[45]={
ja={
{
"その心情には、希望も絶望もなかった。",
},
},
en={
{
"His heart was filled with neither hope nor despair...",
},
},
},
[46]={
ja={
{
"ただ、純粋に。",
},
},
en={
{
"But simply...",
},
},
},
[47]={
ja={
{
"運命という確固な事象だけが、心を占めた。",
},
},
en={
{
"With the absoluteness of destiny.",
},
},
},
[48]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00186",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「あなたならば、僕を送り還すことができる……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「You of all people, may be able to send me back...」",
},
},
},
[49]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00187",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「そのときが、今、この時間、この場所であること……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「Right now, where I stand.」",
},
},
},
[50]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00188",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「それが、僕の運命……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「That is my fate...」",
},
},
},
[51]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00189",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「生の集大成……」",
},
},
en={
{
"「The culmination of my life's work...」",
},
},
},
[52]={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_shr_00190",ch="man"},
},
name={name="砂原",ja="砂原",en="Sahara"},
ja={
{
"「これもひとつの……幸せなのでしょうね」",
},
},
en={
{
"「This too... may be happiness.」",
},
},
},
},
label={
},
}
